snippet.title: Azure Striker GUNVOLT: STRIKER PACK (Switch Version)  - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Azure Striker Gunvolt Striker Pack contains both Azure Striker Gunvolt and Azure Striker Gunvolt 2, two of our flagship games that originally made their home on the Nintendo 3DS. With the release of the Switch version of the Striker Pack, there are a host of new features, improvements, and bonus content that make it the truly complete version of the Azure Striker Gunvolt experience.

Official Website: http://gunvolt.com/en/sp_ns
Twitter (Inti Creates): https://twitter.com/IntiCreatesEN
Facebook (Inti Creates): https://www.facebook.com/inticreates/


Product Details
Title： Azure Striker Gunvolt: Striker Pack
Hardware： Nintendo Switch
Genre： 2D Action 
Release Date (Switch)： August 31st, 2017
Players：1 Player
Developer： Inti Creates

©2017 INTI CREATES CO.,LTD.
